(66, 70, NULL, NULL, '<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: HarmonyOS_Regular; font-size: 22.0032px;\">The 5 megapixels allow you to capture ultra-detailed 3K images. Imou Ranger 2 offers 2 different camera pixel options, so you can choose the one that suits you best.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: HarmonyOS_Regular; font-size: 22.0032px;\">The electric head of Ranger 2 allows it to pan 355° and tilt from -5° to 80°, ensuring that every corner of the room is covered.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: HarmonyOS_Regular; font-size: 22.0032px;\">Ranger 2 keeps an eye on your house, when someone breaks in, the siren will turn on to deter the unwelcome visitor.</span><br>', '1 Year', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-08-22 07:56:41', '2024-08-22 08:07:22'),
(67, 71, NULL, NULL, '<div><ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem 1.15rem; list-style-position: outside; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Neuzeit Grotesk&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(243, 244, 244);\"><li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">COMPACT &amp; EASY-TO-USE - Impressively compact and lightweight, easy to transport and fits into tight spaces. Using it is easy: Just plug into an AC outlet and adjust the brightness and color temperature and get the perfect look in seconds.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">MULTIPLE CONTROL OPTIONS - Onboard controls and an OLED screen make it easy to directly control. With Bluetooth and 2.4G, the FS-60B can easily be controlled with the free NANLINK app for iOS and Android, or with the separately available WS-RC-C2 handheld remote.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">BI-COLOR WITH ADVANCED FEATURES - Adjustable warm-tone range of 2700K-6500K lets you easily dial-in different looks. Advanced features from the top-of-the-line Forza 720B are included: Maximum Output Mode (full power of the light) &amp; Constant Output Mode (maintains constant intensity across the CCT range).</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">FM MOUNT &amp; BOWENS ADAPTER - The native FM Mount allows the FS-60B to be as compact as possible and compatible with separately available modifiers like the Forza Softbox with FM Mount. The included Bowens-Mount adapter provides compatibility with a vast number of light modifiers, such as Nanlite\'s own line of fresnels, softboxes, and umbrellas.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">EYE-CATCHING EFFECTS - Features customizable effects in a simple-to-master menu system, it\'s easy to imitate lighting scenarios that can otherwise be tricky to recreate. At the touch of a button, you can simulate 12 different lighting effects: CCT Loop, INT Loop, Flash, Pulse, Storm, TV, Paparazzi, Candle/Fire, Bad Bulb, Fireworks, Explosion, and Welding.</li></ul></div>', '1 Year', 'https://youtu.be/KEW4q6Nmvpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-08-22 08:33:45', '2024-08-22 08:33:45'),
(68, 72, NULL, NULL, '<div><ul style=\"margin: 0px 0px 1.5rem 1.15rem; list-style-position: outside; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Neuzeit Grotesk&quot;, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(243, 244, 244);\"><li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">POWERFUL, EVEN LIGHT OUTPUT - The daylight-balanced FS-300 LED Monolight from Nanlite utilizes a larger LED array than most COB LED monolights to deliver up to 41040 Lux @ 1m (with the included reflector) as well as a smooth and even light spread with no hotspots when used in a softbox.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">BUILT-IN APP CONTROL AND IN-BODY COOLING - Built-in Bluetooth for direct control with the free NANLINK app for iOS and Android, and 2.4G for more control options. Integrated design with an all-in-one compact fixture makes it more lightweight and more effective at heat dissipation.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">BOWENS STYLE LIGHT MODIFIER MOUNT - By utilizing the near-universal Bowens style light modifier mount and incorporating an umbrella holder into the yolk, the FS-300 is compatible with a massive selection of light modifiers. Including, but not limited to, Nanlite\'s line of fresnels, softboxes, and umbrellas.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">PRACTICAL EFFECTS - With pre-programmed customizable special effects, the FS- 300 makes it easy to imitate lighting scenarios that can otherwise be tricky to recreate. Simulate 11 different practical lighting effects: INT Loop, Flash, Pulse, Storm, TV, Paparazzi, Candle/Fire, Bad Bulb, Firework, Explosion, and Welding.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 5px;\">WE\'VE GOT YOU COVERED - For over 25 years Nanlite has been producing innovative LED lighting solutions backed by a 2-year limited warranty extendible to 3 years limited with registration. Warranty valid only on products purchased from authorized dealers.</li></ul></div>', '1 Year', 'https://youtu.be/KEW4q6Nmvpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-08-22 08:38:28', '2024-08