ckground-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border-radius: 4px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 1px 1px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><div class=\"section-head\" style=\"padding-bottom: 20px;\"><h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 5px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px; line-height: 26px;\">Description</h2></div><div class=\"full-description\" itemprop=\"description\" style=\"line-height: 24px;\"><h2 style=\"margin-bottom: 5px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 20px; line-height: 26px; text-align: justify;\">IMOU Bullet 2E IPC-F22FP 2MP Wi-Fi Camera</h2><div>The IMOU Bullet 2E features Smart Color Night Vision. It comes with four smart night vision modes that provide clear full color or black-and-white pictures even in complete darkness. Advanced IR algorithms provide clear black-and-white pictures even in darkness. Thanks to the two built-in spotlights, your night vision is now lit up and in full color. Color Mode also offers outdoor lighting for your home. Powerful image processing technology quickly finds human targets in images and immediately sends a notification to your smartphone, allowing you to monitor what matters without receiving annoying false alerts. The 1080P sensor and advanced IR algorithms provide crystal clear video both day and night. The cutting-edge H.265 compression reduces network bandwidth and storage usage by 50% at the same video quality. When the camera detects intrusion, with built-in spotlights, Bullet 2E actively keeps unwelcome visitors away from what you care about before you notice them. Dual Antenna and 2x2 MIMO technology resist interference, even at long ranges. IP67 weatherproof design for use in multiple scenarios. It has a 1-year warranty.</div></div></section></div>', '1 Year', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2024-08-22 10:06:26', '2024-08-22 10:06:26'),
